<view class="page home-page">
  <view class="topbar">
    <view class="brand">
      <view class="brand-mark">L</view>
      <text>Linkmai</text>
    </view>
    <text class="top-status">事故处理工作台</text>
  </view>

  <view class="hero card">
    <view>
      <text class="eyebrow">WORKBENCH</text>
      <view class="title">交通事故处理台</view>
      <view class="subcopy">
        以案件为中心，完成材料、赔偿测算和处理文书。
      </view>
    </view>
    <button class="primary-button hero-button" bindtap="startCase">新建案件</button>
  </view>

  <view class="action-grid">
    <button
      wx:for="{{mainActions}}"
      wx:key="label"
      class="action-card {{item.type === 'primary' ? 'action-primary' : ''}}"
      data-path="{{item.path}}"
      bindtap="openAction"
    >
      <view class="action-index">0{{index + 1}}</view>
      <view>
        <view class="action-title">{{item.label}}</view>
        <view class="action-desc">{{item.desc}}</view>
      </view>
    </button>
  </view>

  <view class="card current-card">
    <view class="card-top">
      <view>
        <view class="section-title">当前案件</view>
        <text class="muted case-plate">{{currentCase.title}} · {{currentCase.plate}}</text>
      </view>
      <text class="pill risk-mid">风险 {{currentCase.riskLevel}}</text>
    </view>

    <view class="stage-rail">
      <view wx:for="{{productSteps}}" wx:key="label" class="stage-item {{item.status}}">
        <view class="stage-dot"></view>
        <text>{{item.shortLabel}}</text>
      </view>
    </view>

    <view class="next-box">
      <text class="box-label">下一步</text>
      <view class="next-action">{{currentCase.nextAction}}</view>
      <view class="next-meta">
        <text class="muted">{{currentCase.nextActionTime}}</text>
        <text class="pill">缺 {{currentCase.pendingCount}} 项材料</text>
      </view>
    </view>

    <view class="progress-track">
      <view class="progress-fill" style="width: {{currentCase.progress}}%;"></view>
    </view>

    <button class="secondary-button" bindtap="openCase">继续处理</button>
  </view>

  <view class="warning-panel notice">
    文书和测算均为辅助结果。复杂事故、重伤、酒驾、逃逸等情况将建议人工复核。
  </view>
</view>
